data.description: Welcome to this cute 3 bedroom, 1 bath bungalow home located on a quiet street.  Home features a large great room, eat in kitchen, den with brick fireplace and sliding doors to the screened in porch, laundry room, 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath.  Other amenities include vinyl siding, driveway and large, fenced yard, Conveniently located close to all major roadways and minutes to Trenton, Philadelphia, the Joint Military bases and the Jersey Shore!
